Treat the queen of your heart to a homemade pizza this Mother's Day with 𝐒𝐨𝐟𝐢𝐭𝐞𝐥’𝐬 𝐒𝐭𝐚𝐲 𝐇𝐨𝐦𝐞 𝐑𝐞𝐜𝐢𝐩𝐞 𝐊𝐢𝐭𝐬, a fuss-free easy way to not sweat over the cooking! With a little help, you can now cook delightful classics from Kwee Zeen and The Cliff. Our recipe kits, helmed by our talented chefs, nudge you to becoming a Stay Home Chef!⁣⁣
⁣⁣
